cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CE, cs.SE

The paper deals with the identification and prediction of thermal dynamics in buildings, which is a problem in the field of control engineering and building energy management. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper also proposes the use of nonlinear regression models, which involves machine learning and artificial intelligence techniques, making cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) likely categories as well. The paper also involves simulation and modeling of buildings, which falls under the category of cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science). Finally, the paper involves the implementation of a model-predictive-control system, which falls under the category of cs.SE (Software Engineering).
